# Expense Operating Bad Debt Recoveries Direct To PL Amount

## identifier
de7701

## type
float

## definition
This is the value of bad debt recoveries that have been written back directly to profit and loss during the relevant period.

## syntax
### xbrl
- balance=credit
- name=Expense.Operating.BadDebtRecoveriesDirectToPL.Amount
- classification=baf/bafpr/bafpr2.02.06
- period=duration
